{"tid":1962370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"火車頭我屌你老母","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T17:12:00.000Z","uid":136670,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b11fd221f82397ba92cedd9da00125a46332a834","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"話說今日我想做運動又唔想除口罩<br />\n諗住落街戴口罩踩單車低風險啦<br />\n落一陣又唔係去多人地方戴咗個薄嘅<br />\n又無戴眼鏡<br />\n初頭都無事嘅<br />\n係踩踩下<br />\n遇到個火車頭迎面而黎<br />\n口罩拉咗落去條頸<br />\n我已經提高警覺<br />\n即刻落腳諗住快啲過埋<br />\n點擦肩而過一刻<br />\n佢向我方一噴<br />\n我避都避唔切<br />\n食哂啲煙<br />\n我個様<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係嘟撚住佢個死人嘴「呼～」<br />\n喺我過咗佢嗰一刻個腦已經一遍空白<br />\n聽住佢一下喉嚨嘅抽痰聲<br />\n我差啲喊出嚟<br />\n我&mdash;&mdash;唔&mdash;&mdash;要&mdash;&mdash;有&mdash;&mdash;病&mdash;&mdash;啊&mdash;&mdash;！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">火  車   頭   我   屌   你   老   母</span><br />\n利申：不安到宜家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nBtw<br />\n請大家去like專業清算師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frevengehi%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=87030790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/revengehi/</a><br />\n今日deadline 投稿一個制就得<br />\n<a href=\"https://go.aws/2QUBMbC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.aws%2F2QUBMbC&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ed5caf35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://go.aws/2QUBMbC</a><br />\n<br />\n同民間清算師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vendettists/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvendettists%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=0d282e5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vendettists/</a><br />\n<br />\n利申同佢地無關係"},{"pid":"c2804c5d55a4696389a07cdb54cf298c353d1ed9","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"請大家教我對付廢老"},{"pid":"aebfdac68d9bbd672d542cbaf7a4b67f5a33a775","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"好驚"},{"pid":"33349d5fcf27080962ec03217695788c81bbb039","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"大家記得send email"},{"pid":"42f88da4b2dfd78ab29e71ca954b07aa5dbf39b7","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"天滅中共"},{"pid":"af8e471548cb29d5db4e1c5d391420a06849a325","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"啊！"},{"pid":"a86fd9d1a14399b555a2d897a93dd8a5079a37af","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"睇嚟大家都唔怕火車頭"},{"pid":"d171e0572a70a5de4785e1a833a71e8d16e56da2","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:37:32.000Z","msg":"投稿啊喂"},{"pid":"7adaa787583597eb0381715b1588efb7f3068e29","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"火車頭真可怕"},{"pid":"68a0f14ffe3ed48e9425a4d9d5ba9fc68f5bcbc1","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"大家已原諒火車頭了"},{"pid":"e29a99563250602528c7901386c89ddd7b3dc187","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:38:55.000Z","msg":"投稿啊～"},{"pid":"2896baf726c1c3982f12c8823d934804cce76bec","tid":1962370,"uid":136670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,